{"tid":2053092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【「大波 Man」、高松傑赴英國領事館　撕毀 BNO】","createTime":"2020-06-06T04:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T08:51:58.000Z","uid":5680,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"5af75e740aca79e5792e696acac322c2b6480ced","tid":2053092,"uid":5680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"【「大波 Man」、高松傑赴英國領事館　撕毀 BNO】<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜 3 日表示，如果通過國安法，將讓持 BNO 護照港人留英 12 個月，並獲得進一步工作權利，為日後成為英國公民鋪路。今早（6 日），建制派石房有（大波 Man）、高松傑、公民力量林宇星等人到英國駐港總領事館示威，譴責英國「干涉中國內政」，又指香港人不需要 BNO，他們並且當場將自己各自的 BNO 撕毀。<br />\n<br />\n多人並且在傳媒面前宣誓指，「我在此嚴正聲明，只會持有中華人民共和國香港特別行政區護照，堅定擁護一國兩制，全力支持港區國安法」、「國安港安，反獨反奸！」<br />\n<br />\n林宇星表示，「BNO 對於香港人嚟講只係旅遊證件」，而且不能夠正確代表香港人的國民身份，「我哋已經回歸祖國，睇唔到原因點解要續 BNO」。林又說，希望英國不要再在 BNO 議題上「出口術」，企圖破壞中港關係，以及傷害中港兩地人民感情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3146155442136721/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3146155442136721%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=5deb46ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3146155442136721/?d=n</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cNncYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cNncYg.jpg&h=506c3566&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890d4b4f9df4f87bf7599c26d3e3b3ce689dbbc3","tid":2053092,"uid":5680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3520826484692049/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3520826484692049%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=187b5d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3520826484692049/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"35469cd8f766b18d39bd24e562bd9e90ff234d86","tid":2053092